    "description": "We at Berger Silk Store Advisory Limited are looking for an experienced Store Manager based out of Agra. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Berger Silk Store Advisory Limited:\nBerger Silk Store Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Agra, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Berger Silk Store Advisory Limited!",
